<div class="pad clear">
<h3>Parking</h3>
<p>Car parking charges:<br/>Up to 15 minutes: free<br/>Up to 30 minutes: £1.50<br/>Up to 1 hour: £2.60<br/>Up to 1.5 hours: £3.60<br/>Up to 3 hours: £4.60<br/>Over 3 hours (up to 24 hours): £5.60<br/>Each additional 12 hour period over 24 hours: £2.50<br/><br/>There are five pay machines – two are located in the main hospital entrance, one by the Maternity entrance, one in A&amp;E  and one in the entrance to C Block (Trust HQ)</p>
